of Virginia.

899
00:47:03,080 --> 00:47:05,275
It's in the employee
handbook. In addendum.

900
00:47:06,560 --> 00:47:07,680
In case you haven't read it.

901
00:47:08,320 --> 00:47:10,470
Every time we have a chance
to get ahead...

902
00:47:10,680 --> 00:47:11,829
they move the finish line.

903
00:47:12,000 --> 00:47:13,400
I just follow the rules
around here.

904
00:47:13,600 --> 00:47:15,113
And I expect everyone
who works for me

905
00:47:15,240 --> 00:47:16,240
to follow them as well.

906
00:47:16,400 --> 00:47:19,597
There are no special
circumstances for anyone.

907
00:47:20,080 --> 00:47:22,230
Y'all should be thankful
you have jobs at all.

908
00:47:28,080 --> 00:47:31,550
"For those that cannot attend classes
at the University of Virginia...

909
00:47:31,720 --> 00:47:34,109
"advanced extension courses
are available

910
00:47:34,280 --> 00:47:36,077
"at the Hampton High School."

911
00:47:36,800 --> 00:47:39,075
That's still a
segregated school, Mary.

912
00:47:39,240 --> 00:47:41,708
Virginia acts like Brown
versus Board of Education

913
