00:49:49,400 --> 00:49:50,400
A book.

968
00:49:50,560 --> 00:49:52,915
You have books
in the colored section.

969
00:49:54,240 --> 00:49:55,912
It doesn't have
what I'm looking for.

970
00:49:56,080 --> 00:49:58,230
That's just
the way it is.

971
00:50:02,400 --> 00:50:03,736
Go on, now.
