1009
00:52:11,760 --> 00:52:13,876
I believe
I owe you an apology.

1010
00:52:16,200 --> 00:52:18,509
Well, was that it?

1011
00:52:19,240 --> 00:52:20,992
Can I make it
while we dance?

1012
00:52:33,040 --> 00:52:35,600
I'm afraid I simply misspoke
the other day, Mrs. Goble.

1013
00:52:37,880 --> 00:52:40,110
I've been away
for a long time.

1014
00:52:41,040 --> 00:52:43,873
I imagine I'm just
out of practice.

