00:53:13,960 --> 00:53:15,109
For what, Jim?

1027
00:53:15,920 --> 00:53:17,717
Underestimating you.

1028
00:53:18,600 --> 00:53:20,397
And any other woman
like you...

1029
00:53:22,560 --> 00:53:24,755
Though I don't imagine
there's many.

1030
00:53:26,800 --> 00:53:28,950
That's good practice,
