Dorothy.

1725
01:33:49,720 --> 01:33:51,039
Mrs. Mitchell.

1726
01:33:57,360 --> 01:33:59,191
You're working late today.

1727
01:34:00,160 --> 01:34:02,515
Seems to always
happen that way.

1728
01:34:02,680 --> 01:34:04,671
Yes. Seems to.

1729
01:34:12,520 --> 01:34:13,520
Thank you.

1730
01:34:17,640 --> 01:34:20,393
I hear the IBM's
up to full capacity.

1731
01:34:21,560 --> 01:34:23,198
You certainly
have a knack for it.

1732
01:34:23,880 --> 01:34:26,678
My father taught me a thing
or two about mechanics.

1733
01:34:27,560 --> 01:34:29,755
You know, I have a few
girls in the East Group

