You, either?

1764
01:36:06,960 --> 01:36:09,076
Okay, I'm not gonna
do this all night.

1765
01:36:12,000 --> 01:36:13,479
Oh, mother of mercy.

1766
01:36:14,200 --> 01:36:15,200
That's for me.

1767
01:36:18,520 --> 01:36:20,636
Are you sad, Mama?
No.

